# 5. Step-by-Step Processes

---

## Shared-Nothing Query Execution

```text
Receive query
→ Partition work
→ Execute locally
→ Exchange data
→ Merge results
```

---

## Shared-Disk Coordination

```text
Access data
→ Acquire distributed lock
→ Update local buffer
→ Sync with other nodes
```

---

## NUMA Optimization

```text
Assign worker
→ allocate local memory
→ pin to CPU
→ avoid remote access
```

---

