# 8. Common Confusions

### Shared Memory vs NUMA

* both share memory
* NUMA has unequal access time

---

### Shared Nothing vs Shared Disk

* SN → no sharing
* SD → shared storage

---

### Parallelism vs Concurrency

* concurrency = many tasks
* parallelism = many CPUs

